on Gorst|Sir John Eldon Gorst]]\n  | after=[[George W. E. Russell]]\n  | years=1891\u201392\n}}\n{{succession box\n  | title=[[Under-Secretary of State for Foreign Affairs]]\n  | before=[[Edward Grey, 1st Viscount Grey of Fallodon|Sir Edward Grey, Bt]]\n  | years=1895\u201398\n  | after=[[St John Brodrick, 1st Earl of Midleton|Hon. St John Brodrick]]\n}}\n{{s-bef | before = [[Edward Stanley, 17th Earl of Derby|The Earl of Derby]] | as = Chairman of the Joint War Air Committee}}\n{{s-ttl | title  = [[Secretary of State for Air|President of the Air Board]] | years  = 1916\u20131917}}\n{{s-aft | after  = [[Weetman Pearson, 1st Viscount Cowdray|The Viscount Cowdray]]}}\n\n{{s-bef |rows=3| before = [[Robert Crewe-Milnes, 1st Marquess of Crewe|The Marquess of Crewe]]}}\n{{s-ttl | title  = [[Lord Privy Seal]] | years = 1915\u20131916}}\n{{s-aft | after  = [[David Lindsay, 27th Earl of Crawford|The Earl of Crawford]]}}\n{{s-ttl | title  = [[Leader of the House of Lords]] | years = 1916\u20131924}}\n{{s-aft | after  = [[Richard Haldane, 1st Viscount Haldane|The Viscount Haldane]]}}\n{{s-ttl | title  = [[Lord President of the Council]] | years = 1916\u20131919}}\n{{s-aft | after  = [[Arthur Balfour|Arthur James Balfour]]}}\n{{succession box\n | before=[[Arthur Balfour|Arthur James Balfour]]\n | title=[[Secretary of State for Foreign Affairs|Foreign Secretary]]\n | years=1919\u20131924\n | after=[[Ramsay MacDonald]]\n}}\n{{succession box\n |before=[[Charles Cripps, 1st Baron Parmoor|The Lord Parmoor]]\n |title=[[Lord President of the Council]]\n |years=1924\u20131925\n |after=[[Arthur Balfour|Arthur James Balfour]]\n}}\n{{succession box\n |before=[[Richard Burdon Haldane, 1st Viscount Haldane|The Viscount Haldane]]\n |title=[[Leader of the House of Lords]]\n |years=1924\u20131925\n |after=[[James Gascoyne-Cecil, 4th Marquess of Salisbury|The 4th Marquess of Salisbury]]\n}}\n{{s-gov}}\n{{succession box\n | before=[[Victor Alexander Bruce, 9th Earl of Elgin|The Earl of Elgin]]\n